.TH SDL_Color 3type "SDL 3.1.2" "Simple Directmedia Layer" "SDL3 DATATYPES"
.SH NAME
SDL_Color \- A structure that represents a color as RGBA components\[char46]
.SH HEADER FILE
Defined in SDL3/SDL_pixels\[char46]h

.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
.B #include \(dqSDL3/SDL.h\(dq
.PP
.BI "typedef struct SDL_Color
.BI "{
.BI "    Uint8 r;
.BI "    Uint8 g;
.BI "    Uint8 b;
.BI "    Uint8 a;
.BI "} SDL_Color;
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
The bits of this structure can be directly reinterpreted as an
integer-packed color which uses the

.BR SDL_PIXELFORMAT_RGBA32
 format
(
.BR SDL_PIXELFORMAT_ABGR8888
 on little-endian
systems and 
.BR SDL_PIXELFORMAT_RGBA8888
 on
big-endian systems)\[char46]

.SH AVAILABILITY
This struct is available since SDL 3\[char46]0\[char46]0\[char46]

